Families, workers and small businesses in West Virginia and across the country are counting on Congress to get #taxreform done.
It’s time to seize this important once-in-a-generation opportunity. It’s time to get #taxreform across the finish line. It’s time to send this pro-growth legislation to @POTUS’ desk.
West Virginians want #taxreform because they know what it will do for our state.

Today, we are closer than ever before to getting comprehensive, pro-growth #taxreform across the finish line. So many West Virginians are rooting for this effort because it will make a positive difference in their lives.
#Taxreform will also increase the #ChildTaxCredit for families, make American businesses more competitive globally and lead to higher wages and more opportunities for our workers.
#Taxreform will nearly double the standard deduction that is already used by 83% of West Virginians.
